name: SVGLineElement
description: The SVGLineElement interface provides access to the properties of <line> elements, as well as methods to manipulate them.

members.name: SVGLineElement.x1
members.description: Returns an SVGAnimatedLength that corresponds to attribute x1 on the given <line> element.

members.name: SVGLineElement.y1
members.description: Returns an SVGAnimatedLength that corresponds to attribute y1 on the given <line> element.

members.name: SVGLineElement.x2
members.description: Returns an SVGAnimatedLength that corresponds to attribute x2 on the given <line> element.

members.name: SVGLineElement.y2
members.description: Returns an SVGAnimatedLength that corresponds to attribute y2 on the given <line> element.
